{
  "stem": "22840.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That they frightened them very much by their mere appearance-- armed, unkempt men, with hand grenades hanging from their clothes, with guns.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Not real calmed, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Coming in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "His version is that he threatened them that if they will not keep me well, they will come and kill them and burn the house on them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I recall from the time, and I recall it very clearly, only a deep care by that family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Doing things that-- that clearly show that they wanted to save me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And from what I know now, I believe that my version is the correct one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Yes, they may have been frightened, without any doubt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Yes, they may have been threatened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But I don't think they were totally unwilling participants.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That village has more than me saved, including a neighbor which saved somebody Jewish-- a woman with her child.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This is the bright side of-- of the Holocaust, if there's any bright side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember being placed there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They gave me food on my arrival.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That, I recall very, very well, because I didn't know what I was eating.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was very good, and I didn't know at the time what it was, and they never served it again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And when I asked for it, they told me it was sausages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they cannot serve it again, because they have none.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There are no sausages available anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I'm sure they were not kosher, but I don't think it was a concern of mine at the time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But I felt very much wanted, and I felt very much loved by them.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
